title: #143 - Chris Porter & ME
description: Comedian Chris Porter and I hang out in the Mancave and talk about hanging w/ Kid Rock, Last Comic Standing, dick comics, how great Nick Dipaolo is, and I explain how I owe my success to him and Earthquake!
